STATE
v.
GIBSON 2019-0261 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 21, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

Appellant has not filed a memorandum in support of jurisdiction, due May 17, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed.
